1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,290
[Episode 28]

2
00:00:01,290 --> 00:00:04,090
Fuzhi
Why don't I have an egg on my plate?

3
00:00:04,980 --> 00:00:06,250
You know what?

4
00:00:06,870 --> 00:00:09,800
I never give my eggs to others.

5
00:00:10,320 --> 00:00:14,750
Except for my brother, you're the second person.

6
00:00:15,820 --> 00:00:16,450
Want it?

7
00:00:16,550 --> 00:00:19,900
Fuzhi, aren't you Japanese?

8
00:00:20,960 --> 00:00:22,520
Ah, here you go.

9
00:00:22,850 --> 00:00:25,690
Just eat and talk less.

10
00:00:26,030 --> 00:00:27,650
They look good together.

11
00:00:28,180 --> 00:00:28,730
Shut up.

12
00:00:31,090 --> 00:00:33,090
I can definitely do better than him.

13
00:00:33,490 --> 00:00:34,620
Taji.

14
00:00:48,360 --> 00:00:50,560
[Mission 1: Spend Money]

15
00:01:04,470 --> 00:01:07,500
Since Fuzhi is so close to Bin

16
00:01:07,890 --> 00:01:10,210
I need to get even closer.

17
00:01:13,730 --> 00:01:15,570
What the hell is going on?

18
00:01:24,210 --> 00:01:26,440
That student wearing black sunglasses
Why isn't he sitting down?

19
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:28,600
[Mission 2: Ship the Couple]

20
00:01:33,170 --> 00:01:35,390
Here, let me carry your bag.

21
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:44,920
[Mission 3: Take Care]

22
00:01:48,820 --> 00:01:52,580
Ah, missed the braised eggs again.

23
00:01:53,350 --> 00:01:57,210
You can have mine.

24
00:01:58,050 --> 00:01:58,970
Please take it.

25
00:01:59,690 --> 00:02:02,610
Your language skills are quite good this time.

26
00:02:11,450 --> 00:02:13,850
No need, I can walk by myself.

27
00:02:30,820 --> 00:02:33,610
You're following me quite closely, everywhere I go.

28
00:02:33,610 --> 00:02:38,410
Interested
In joining me in the bathroom?

29
00:02:43,130 --> 00:02:46,060
This trick really works
No need to follow me anymore.

30
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:51,079
[To Be Continued]
